data.description: *Seller to pay full initiation fee with acceptable offer*  Welcome home!  This 4 bedroom, 2 ½ bath, 2 car garage with golf cart stall is ready for you to move in!  Located in Eagles Bluff, this home is the perfect size for low maintenance living.  The spacious living area with fireplace and built-ins is open to the dining room and kitchen, allowing for an ease in entertaining or everyday living.  Large primary bedroom with sitting area and ensuite bath is a quiet retreat.  Primary bath is appointed with separate vanities, tub and separate shower, and large walk-in closet!   Two guest rooms share a Jack n Jill bath and provide ample space for family or guests.  The fourth bedroom makes an excellent office or flex space.  Completing the interior of the home is a half bath and utility room!  Outside is a fabulous screened-in porch with outside kitchen and hot tub!  Eagle’s Bluff is a private retreat on Lake Palestine.  It is a 462 acre private sanctuary accented by 50 foot towering trees, creeks, ponds, and lake that frame the breathtaking homesites, welcoming Clubhouse, and signature 18-hole championship golf course.  Check out Eagle’s Bluff website at eaglesbluffcc. com for more info.  Buyer to satisfy self on all fees.  Come See!  Come Buy!
